repository-code: "https://github.com/jbenhart44/Research-Toolkit"
url: "https://jbenhart44.github.io"
abstract: >
  A collection of 14 Claude Code commands that structure AI-assisted
  research workflows — verification (/pcv, /pace, /coa, /audit), workflow
  bookkeeping (/startup, /dailysummary, /weeklysummary, /commit, /simplify,
  /improve), content generation (/quarto, /readable), and triage
  (/help, /review). Implements Spec-Driven Development patterns for
  empirical research: plan-construct-verify with explicit specifications,
  multi-agent cross-checking, and verifiable citation/numerical audits.
keywords:
  - "claude-code"
  - "spec-driven-development"
  - "research-tooling"
  - "verification"
  - "llm-agents"
